Troll v 1.0
Needed for this to work:
Jquery

HOWTO:
Include this in in 
<head>
	<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.7.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
	<script src="troll-1.0.js" type="text/javascript"></script>	
</head>

EXAMPLE:
<div id="content" class="classname tl:background(red)"> OR
<div id="content" class="tl:background(red)">

Will result in a background color red for divs

TODOS:
Fix multi injections like this:
<div id="content" class="tl:background(red), border(1px solid red)">

WHY:
Simple, with use of a grid system we can include the style like poistioning or colors after grid_XX directly in our class. This will save time and so on...

Have fun!